    "To mitigate this, additional filtering mechanisms, such as metadata checks or contractspecific identifiers, are required to ensure that the system retrieves the most contextually appropriate information from the correct contract section.",
    "To overcome this issue, several strategies can be applied.",
    "One approach is to add metadata to the chunks and, when accessing the vectorstore, use this metadata to filter the information returned.",
    "This method improves the relevance of the retrieved texts by narrowing the search to only those chunks that match specific metadata criteria.",
    "displays the most relevant metadata attributes for the contracts: source, contract, and clause."
